data.description: Charming one and a half story home with gorgeous woodwork and oversized, heated garage.  This home is cute, cute, cute!  Main floor features, living room, dining room, 2 bedrooms, a bathroom, kitchen and a brand new mud room area.  You will love the bonus space this house has with the front porch and bonus bedroom upstairs.  Basement has non conforming bedroom, tons of storage space, a rec area and a full bathroom.  Call your favorite agent today for a private tour.
